  "title": "Remnant Bosses",
  "description": "Face the deadliest bosses ever forged combat, fights, and chaos await!",
  "body": "<!-- Header Images -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WFXnzNx.png\" alt=\"Header 1\" style=\"margin-right:10px;\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Social Badges -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://nightbeam.gitbook.io/remnants/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Documentation&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=read-the-docs&logoColor=white\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Section Divider -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" alt=\"About Header\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- YouTube Video -->\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/8djzQBruLto\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<!-- About Section -->\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n  Born from the depths of the underworld, the <strong>Remnants</strong> combines the resilience of the undead with the lethal precision of an ancient combat master. Whether you’re a seasoned adventurer or a thrill-seeker looking for your next big fight, this mod delivers a heart-pounding experience.\n</p>\n\n<!-- Ko-fi Button -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" width=\"240\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\" style=\"border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Features Header -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" alt=\"Features\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- Boss Section -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#e03e2d;\">Remnant Ossukage</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;\">\n  A mysterious skeletal shinobi who commands the battlefield with speed, deception, and deadly precision.\n</p>\n\n<h3>Abilities</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Shadow Dash:</strong> Rapid high-speed charge attack that pierces through players.</li>\n  <li><strong>Kunai Barrage:</strong> Throws spinning kunai projectiles with custom flight animations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Teleport Strike:</strong> Briefly vanishes and reappears behind unsuspecting players.</li>\n  <li><strong>Phase Shift Mode:</strong> Gains new patterns and enhanced speed when enraged.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Fight Experience</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perfect for dungeon arenas or late-game progression.</li>\n  <li>Features <strong>custom textures, models, animations, and SFX</strong> (dash, attacks, theme music).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Minions Section -->\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#3598db;\">Skeleton Minions</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;\">\n  The Ossukage is accompanied by undead minions that support him in battle.\n</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Melee Skeleton Fighters:</strong> Rush attackers with fast movement.</li>\n  <li><strong>Guardian Minions:</strong> Protect the boss during vulnerable phases.</li>\n  <li><strong>Wave Summons:</strong> Additional minions spawn based on boss health thresholds.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#e03e2d;\">Mutated Rats</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;\">\n  Scurry through ruins, caves, and dungeons, adding danger even before the boss fight.\n</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Default Rat, Grey Rat, Yellow Rat, Blue Rat</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Banner Images -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n  <a href=\"https://builtbybit.com/resources/brainrot-monster-pack-vol-1.73973\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8699b70f53dfa1fc1d907589e24564027bb64c26.png\" alt=\"Banner 1\" style=\"margin-right:10px;\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://builtbybit.com/resources/brainrot-monster-pack-vol-2.76296\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8874ac9cb5749b4f1c4e6e07036224137838b414.png\" alt=\"Banner 2\"></a>\n</p>\n",
